description:
With this DLC you will unlock:

- stylized pink hair bun 
- stylized blue hair bun 
- long hair with reverse blue ombre
- long hair with reverse pink ombre
- casual brown hair bun 
- casual dark hair bun 
- casual long dark hair
- casual long blonde hair
- white jeans
- orange jeans
- violet sweater
- pink sweater with white polka dots 
- 1500 coins to change the look of your doll's house

Allow your creativity to create more styles for your paper princess!
name: DIY Paper Doll: Daily Style
